hadiths[103]{hadithnumber,text}:
7268,"aik Yahudi ( Kab ahbaar Islam laney se pahley) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aey ameerul-momineen ! agar hamarey yahan sura Mayeda ki ye aayat nazil hoti ( اليوم أكملت لكم دينكم وأتممت عليكم نعمتي ورضيت لكم الإسلام (ke '' aaj maine tumharey liye tumharey Deen ko mukammal kar diya aur tum par apni nemat ko pura kar diya aur tumharey liye Islam ko bataur Deen ke pasand kar liya. '' to ham us din ko eid ( khushi (ka din bana letey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main janta hun ke ye aayat kis din nazil hui thi, Arfa ke din nazil hui aur Juma ka din tha. imam Bukhari ne kaha ye riwayat Sufiyan ne Misar se suni , Misar ne Qais se suna aur Qais ne Tariq se."
7269,"unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se wo khutba suna jo unhon-ne wafat nabwi ke doosrey din padha tha, jis din musalmanon ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se bait ki thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par chadhey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se pahley khutba padha phir kaha : ammaa ba'd! Allah Taala ne apne rasool ke liye wo cheez (aakhirat) pasand ki jo uske paas thi iske bajaey jo tumharey paas thi yani duniya aur ye kitabullah maujood hai jiske zariey Allah Taala ne tumharey rasool ko Deen w seedha rasta batlaya to usey tum thaamey raho to hidayat yaab rahogey . yani us rastey par rahogey jo Allah ne apne paighambar ko batlaya tha."
7270,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apne seeney se lagaya aur farmaya ''aey Allah ! usey Quran ka ilm sikhaa .''
7271,Allah Taala ne tumhen Islam aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zariey ghanii (maaldaar) kar diya hai ya buland darja kar diya hai.
7272,wo uski bait qabool kartey hain aur ye likha ke main tera hukm sununga aur maanoonga basharte ke Allah ki shariiat aur uske rasool ki sunnat ke muwafiq ho jahan tak mujh se mumkin hoga.
7273,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mujhey (jawaameul-kalim) (mukhtasar alfaz mein bahut se maana ko sumon dena (ke sath bheja gaya hai aur meri madad raub ke zariey ki gaee aur main soyaa hua tha ke maine khuwab mein dekha ke mere paas zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan rakh di gaiin.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to chaley gaey aur tum mazey kar rahe ho ya usi jaisa koi kalima kahaa.
7274,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''anbiyaa mein se koi Nabi aisa nahi jinko kuchh nishaniyan (yani moa'jazaat ( na diye gaey hon jinke mutabiq un par eman laya gaya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) insan eman laey aur mujhey jo bada moa'jza diya gaya wo Quran Majeed hai jo Allah ne meri taraf bhejaa. isliye main ummeed karta hun ke qiyamat ke din shumaar mein tamam anbiya se zyada pairwi karne waley mere hongey.''
7275,"us masjid (khaana ka'ba) mein, main Sheba bin Usman Hajabi (jo Kaba ke kaleed-bardaar they) ke paas betha to unhon-ne kaha ke jahan tum baithey ho, wahin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mere paas baithey they aur unhon-ne kaha tha ke mera irada hai ke Kaba mein kisi tarah ka sona chandi na chhodun aur sab musalmanon mein taqseem kar dun jo nazarullaah Kaba mein jama hai. maine kaha ke aap aisa nahi kar saktey. kahan kyon? maine kaha ke aap ke donon sathiyon (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne aisa nahi kya tha. is par unhon-ne kaha ke wo donon buzurg aisey hi they jinki iqtida (pairvi) karni hi chahiye"
7276,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amanat daari aasman se kuchh logon ke dilon ki jadoon mein utrii, (yani unki fitrat mein dakhil hai) aur Quran Majeed nazil hua to unhon-ne Quran Majeed ka matlab samjha aur sunnat ka ilm hasil kya to Quran w hadis donon se us emaandari ko jo fitratii thi poori quwwat mil gaee."
7277,sabse achi baat kitabullah aur sabse achchha tariqa (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tariqa hai aur sabse buri nai baat ( bidat ( paida karna hai) Deen mein) aur bila shubah jiska tum se wada kya jata hai wo aa kar rahegi aur tum parwardigar se bach kar kahin nahi ja saktey.
7278,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yaqeenan main tumharey darmyan kitabullah se faisla karoonga.''
7279,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yaqeenan main tumharey darmyan kitabullah se faisla karoonga.''
7280,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''saarii ummat jannat mein jaeygi siwaey unke jinhoney inkar kya.'' sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! inkar kon karega? farmaya ''jo meri itaat karega wo jannat mein dakhil hoga aur jo meri nafarmani karega us ne inkar kya.''
7281,"Farishtey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey (Jibraaiil aur meekaaiil) aur aap soey huey they. aik ne kaha ke ye soey huey hain, doosrey ne kaha ke unki aankhen so rahi hain lekin unka dil bedaar hai. unhon-ne kaha ke tumharey un sahib (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ki aik misal hai isliye unki misal bayan karo. to unmein se aik ne kaha ke ye so rahe hain, doosrey ne kaha ke aankh so rahi hai aur dil bedaar hai. unhon-ne kaha ke unki misal us shakhs jaisi hai jisne aik ghar banaya aur wahan khaney ki dawat ki aur bulaney waley ko bhejaa, isliye jisne bulaney waley ki dawat qabool kar li wo ghar mein dakhil ho gaya aur dastar-khuwaan se khaya aur jisne bulaney waley ki dawat qabool nahi ki wo ghar mein dakhil nahi hua aur dastar-khuwaan se khana nahi khaayaa, phir unhon-ne kaha ke uski unke liye tafseer kar do taake ye samajh jaaein. kuchh ne kaha ke ye to soey huey hain lekin kuchh ne kaha ke aankhen to so rahi hain lekin dil bedaar hai. phir unhon-ne kaha ke ghar to jannat hai aur bulaney waley Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain, isliye jo unki itaat karega wo Allah ki itaat karega aur jo unki nafarmani karega wo Allah ki nafarmani karega aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) achchhey aur burey logon ke darmyan farq karne waley hain. Muhammad-bin-Ubaada ke sath is hadis ko Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne bhi Leis se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Khaalid-bin-Yazeed-misrii se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin- abii-Hilaal se, unhon-ne Jaabir se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham par bedaar huey, phir yahi hadis naql ki"
7282,"aey Quran aur hadis padhney waalo! tum agar Quran aur hadis par na jamoo gey, idhar-udhar daaiin-baaiin rasta logey to bhi gumrah hogey bahut hi badey gumraah."
7283,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ''meri aur jis dawat ke sath mujhey Allah Taala ne bheja hai uski misal aik aisey shakhs jaisi hai jo kisi qaum ke paas aaey aur kahey : aey qaum ! maine aik lashkar apni aankhon se dekha hai aur main saaf tour per tum ko daraane wala hun, isliye bachao ki sura karo to us qaum ke aik giroh ne baat maan li aur raat ke shuru hi mein nikal bhaagey aur hifazat ki jagah chaley gaey. isliye nijat pa gaey lekin unki dusri jamat ne jhutlaayaa aur apni jagah hi par maujood rahe, phir subah sawerey hi dushman ke lashkar ne unhein aa liya aur unhein maara aur unko barbad kar diya. to ye misal hai uski jo meri itaat karein aur jo dawat main laya hon iski pairwi karein aur uski misal hai jo meri nafarmani karein aur jo haq main lekar aaya hun usey jhuttlaaye."
7284,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui aur aap ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaleefa banaya gaya aur Arab ke kai qabaayel phir gaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse ladna chaha to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap logon se kis buniyad par jang karengey jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon se us waqt tak jang karun jab tak wo kalima la ilaaha-illallaah ka iqrar na kar lein isliye jo shakhs iqrar kar ley ke la ilaaha-illallaah to meri taraf se uska maal aur uski jaan mehfooz hai. albatta kisi haq ke badal ho to wo aur baat hai (maslan kisi ka maal mar ley ya kisi ka khoon karey) ab iske baqi aamaal ka hisab Allah ke hawale hai lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! main to us shakhs se jang karunga jisne Namaz aur zakat mein farq kya hai kyonke zakat maal ka haq hai, Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey aik rassii bhi deney se rukeyn gey jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko detey they, to main unse unke inkar par bhi jang karunga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir jo maine ghaur kya to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein ladai ka sujhaaw daala hai to maine jaan liya ke wo haq par hain. abu-Bukair aur Abdullaah-bin-Saaleh ne Leis se oonaaqaa (عناقا) (ki bajaey (عقلا)) kaha yani bakri ka bachcha aur yahi zyada sahi hai."
7285,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui aur aap ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaleefa banaya gaya aur Arab ke kai qabaayel phir gaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse ladna chaha to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap logon se kis buniyad par jang karengey jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon se us waqt tak jang karun jab tak wo kalima la ilaaha-illallaah ka iqrar na kar lein isliye jo shakhs iqrar kar ley ke la ilaaha-illallaah to meri taraf se uska maal aur uski jaan mehfooz hai. albatta kisi haq ke badal ho to wo aur baat hai (maslan kisi ka maal mar ley ya kisi ka khoon karey) ab iske baqi aamaal ka hisab Allah ke hawale hai lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! main to us shakhs se jang karunga jisne Namaz aur zakat mein farq kya hai kyonke zakat maal ka haq hai, Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey aik rassii bhi deney se rukeyn gey jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko detey they, to main unse unke inkar par bhi jang karunga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir jo maine ghaur kya to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein ladai ka sujhaaw daala hai to maine jaan liya ke wo haq par hain. abu-Bukair aur Abdullaah-bin-Saaleh ne Leis se oonaaqaa (عناقا) (ki bajaey (عقلا)) kaha yani bakri ka bachcha aur yahi zyada sahi hai."
7286,"Uena-bin-Huzaifa-bin-badr Madina aaey aur apne bhateejey  hurra-bin-Qais-bin-Hisn ke yahan qiyam kya. hurra-bin- Qais un logon mein se they jinhein umr (Raziallahu anhu) apne qareeb rakhtey they. Quran Majeed ke ulma umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke shareeke-majlis aur mashwara rahtey they, chahe wo boodhey hon ya jawaan. phir Uena ne apne bhatijey hurr se kaha : bhatijey ! kya ameerul-momineen ke yahan kuchh rusookh hasil hai ke tum mere liye unke yahan haziri ki ijazat ley do? unhon-ne kaha ke main aap ke liye ijazat maangon ga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir unhon-ne Uena ke liye ijazat chahi (aur aap ne ijazat di) phir jab Uena majlis mein pahunchey to kaha ke aey ibne-khattaab, Allah ki qism ! tum hamein bahut zyada nahi detey aur na hamarey darmyan insaf ke sath faisla kartey ho. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ghussa ho gaey, yahan tak ke aap ne unhein saza dene ka irada kar liya. itney mein hurraa ne kaha : ameerul-momineen ! Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya (خذ العفو وأمر بالعرف وأعرض an (an) الجاهلين‏) ke ''muaaf karne ka tariqa ikhtiyar karo aur bhalai ka hukm do aur jaahilon se bacha karo. ''aur ye shakhs jaahilon mein se hai. isliye Allah ki qism ! umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney jab ye aayat unhon-ne tilawat ki to aap thandey ho gaey aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aadat thi ke Allah ki kitab par fauran amal kartey."
7287,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaee. jab suraj girahan hua tha aur log Namaz padh rahe they Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi khadi Namaz padh rahi thin. maine kaha logon ko kya ho gaya hai (ke be waqt Namaz padh rahe hain) to unhon-ne hath se aasman ki taraf ishara kya aur kaha : Subhan-Allah ! maine kaha koi nishani hai? unhon-ne sar se ishara kya ke haan. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur sana ke baad farmaya ''koii cheez aisi nahi lekin maine aaj us jagah se usey dekh liya, yahan tak ke jannat aur dozakh bhi aur mujhey wahi ki gaee hai ke tum log qabron mein bhi aazmaey jaaogey., dajjal ke fitney ke qareeb-qareeb isliye momin ya Muslim mujhey yaqin nahi ke Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne unmein se kon sa lafz kaha tha to wo (qabr mein farishton ke sawal par kahega ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas roshan nishanat lekar aaey aur ham ne unki dawat qabool ki aur eman laey. us se kaha jaeyga ke aaraam se sotey raho, hamein malum tha ke tum momin ho aur munafiq ya shak mein mubtala mujhey yaqin nahi ke unmein se kon sa lafz Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha tha, to wo kahega (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mutaalliq sawal par ke) mujhey malum nahi, maine logon ko jo kehtey suna wahi maine bhi bak diya."
7288,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab tak main tum se yaksoo rahoon tum bhi mujhey chhod do (aur sawalat wghaira na karo) kyonke tum se pahley ki ummatein apne (ghair zaroori ( sawal aur anbiya ke samney ikhtilaf ki wjah se tabah ho gaiin. isliye jab main tumhen kisi cheez se rokoon to tum bhi us se parhez karo aur jab main tumhen kisi baat ka hukm dun to bajaa lao jis had tak tum mein taqat ho.''
7289,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse bada mujrim wo musalman hai jisne kisi aisi cheez ke mutaalliq puchha jo haram nahi thi aur uske sawal ki wjah se wo haram kar di gaii.''
7290,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjide-Nabawi mein chatai se gher kar aik hujra bana liya aur Ramazan ki raaton mein iske andar Namaz padhney lagey phir aur log bhi jama ho gaey to aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz nahi aai. logon ne samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey hain. isliye unmein se kuchh khaakhaarney lagey taake aap bahar tashrif laaein. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tum logon ke kaam se waaqif (واقف) hun, yahan tak ke mujhey dar hua ke kahin tum par ye namaaze-Taraaveeh farz na kar di jaey aur agar farz kar di jaey to tum usey qaaim nahi rakh sako gey. isliye aey logo ! apne gharon mein ye Namaz padho kyonke farz Namaz ke siwa insan ki sabse afzal Namaz uske ghar mein hai."
7291,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh chizon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya jinhein aap ne na-pasand kya jab logon ne bahut zyada poochhna shuru kar diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naraz huey aur farmaya : poochho! is par aik sahabi khadey huey aur puchha : ya Rasulullah ! mere walid kon hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey walid Huzafa hain. phir doosra shakhs khada hua aur puchha mere walid kon hain? farmaya ke tumharey walid Sheba ke Maula Salim hain. phir jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra par ghussa ke aasaar mehsus kiye to arz kya ham izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki bargah mein aapko ghussa dilaane se tauba kartey hain.
7292,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke jo tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai wo mujhey likhiye to unhon-ne unhein likha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har Namaz ke baad kehtey they لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وحده لا شريك له ، Mina له الملك وله الحمد ، Mina وهو على كل شىء قدير ، Mina اللهم لا مانع لما أعطيت ، Mina wla معطي لما منعت ، Mina wla ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد ''tanhaa Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, iska koi Sharik nahi, mulk usi ka hai aur tamam tareef usi ke liye hain aur wo har cheez par qaadir hai ! aey Allah jo to ata karey usey koi rokney wala nahi aur jisey to rokey usey koi dene wala nahi aur kisi naseeb waaley ka naseeb terey muqable mein usey nafa nahi pahuncha sakega aur unhein ye bhi likha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) be-faayeda bahut sawal karne se mana kartey they aur maal zaaye karne se aur aap maaon ki nafarmani karne se mana kartey they aur ladkiyon ko zinda dargor karne se aur apna haq mehfooz rakhney aur dusron ka haq na deney se aur be-zaroorat maangney se mana farmatey they."
7293,"ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, to aap ne farmaya ke hamein takalluf ikhtiyar karne se mana kya gaya hai."
7294,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suraj dhalney ke baad bahar tashrif laey aur Zohar ki Namaz padhi, phir salam pherney ke baad aap member par khadey huey aur qiyamat ka zikr kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zikr kya ke is se pahley badey-badey waaqiaat hongey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se jo shakhs kisi cheez ke mutaalliq sawal karna chahey to sawal kare. aaj mujh se jo sawal bhi karogey main uska jawab doonga jab tak main apni us jagah par hun. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par log bahut zyada roney lagey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baar-baar wahi farmatey they ke mujh se poochho . unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir koi shakhs khada hua aur poochha, meri jagah kahan hai. ( jannat ya jahannam mein) ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke jahannam mein. phir Abdullah-bin Huzafa (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha mere walid kon hain ya Rasulullah ? farmaya ke tumharey walid Huzafa hain. bayan kya ke phir aap musalsal kehtey rahe ke mujh se poochho , mujh se poochho , aakhir mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ghutnon ke bal baith kar kaha : ham Allah se rab ki haisiyat se, Islam se Deen ki haisiyat se, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se rasool ki haisiyat se razi w khush hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kalimaat kahey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, abhi mujh par jannat aur dozakh us diwar ki chaudai mein mere samney ki gaee thi (yani unki tasweerein) jab main Namaz padh raha tha, aaj ki tarah maine khair w shar ko nahi dekha."
7295,aik sahib ne kaha : ya Nabi Allah ! mere walid kon hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey walid falan hain. aur ye aayat nazil huii يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تسألوا an (an) أشياء ''aey logo ! aisi cheezein na poochho.''
7296,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' insan barabar sawal karta rahega , yahan tak ke sawal karega ke ye to Allah hai, har cheez ka paida karne wala lekin Allah ko kis ne paida kya.''"
7297,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke aik khet mein tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ki aik shaakh par tek lagaey huey they ke Yahudi idhar se guzrey to unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke unse Rooh ke barey mein poochho . lekin dusron ne kaha ke unse na poochho . kahin aisi baat na suna dein jo tumhen na-pasand hai. aakhir aap ke paas wo log aaey aur kaha : abul-Qaasim ! Rooh ke barey mein hamein bataiye ? phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der khadey dekhtey rahe mein samajh gaya ke aap par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. main thodi door hat gaya, yahan tak ke wahi ka nuzool pura ho gaya, phir aap ne ye aayat ( ويسألونك an (an) الروح قل الروح من أمر ربي‏ ( padhi ''aur aap Rooh ke barey mein poochhtey hain, kahey ke Rooh mere rab ke hukm mein se hai.''"
7298,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki aik anguthi banwaai to doosrey logon ne bhi soney ki anguthiyan banwaa liin, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine soney ki aik anguthi banwaai thi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phenk di aur farmaya ke main usey kabhi nahi pahnoonga aur logon ne bhi apni anguthiyan phenk din."
7299,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) (iftaar w sahar ke baghair kai din ke rozey) na rakha karo. sahaba ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) rakhtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tum jaisa nahi hun. mein raat guzaarta hun aur mera rab mujhey khilaataa-pilaataa hai lekin log saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) se nahi rukey. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath 2 din ya 2 raaton mein saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) kya, phir logon ne chaand dekh liya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar chaand na nazar aata to main aur wisaal karta, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka maqsad unhein sarzanish karna tha."
7300,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein iint ke baney huey member par khada ho kar khutba diya. aap talwaar liye huey they jis mein aik saheefa latkaa hua tha. aap ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! hamarey paas kitabullah ke siwa koi aur kitab nahi jisey padha jaey aur siwa is saheefa ke. phir unhon-ne usey khola to usmein diyat mein diye janey waley oonton ki umaron ka bayan tha. (ke diyat mein itni itnii umr ke oont diye jaaein) aur is mein ye bhi tha ke Madina taiba ki zameen eir pahaadii se saur pahaadii tak haram hai. to usmein jo koi nai baat (bid'at) nikaaleyga is par Allah ki laanat hai aur farishton ki aur tamam logon ki. Allah us se kisi farz ya nafl ibadat ko qabool nahi karega aur is mein ye bhi tha ke musalmanon ki zimme-dari (ahad ya amaan) aik hai iska zimme daar unmein sabse adnaa musalman bhi ho sakta hai to jisne kisi musalman ka zimma todaa, is par Allah ki laanat hai aur farishton ki aur tamam logon ki. Allah uski na farz ibadat qabool karega aur na nafl ibadat aur is mein ye bhi tha ke jisne kisi se apni waaliyon ki ijazat ke baghair 'walaa' ka rishta qaaim kya is par aur farishton aur tamam insanon ki laanat hai, Allah na uski farz Namaz qabool karega na nafl."
7301,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi kaam kya jis se kuchh logon ne parhez karna ikhtiyar kya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un logon ka kya haal hoga jo aisi cheez se parhez kartey hain jo main karta hun, Allah ki qism ! main unse zyada Allah ke mutaalliq ilm rakhta hun aur unse zyada Allah ka dar rakhta hun."
7302,"ummat ke 2 behtreen insan qareeb tha ke halaak ho jatey (yani Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu)) jis waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bani Tameem ka wafad aaya to unmein se aik sahib ( umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bani majaashea' mein se Aqra-bin-Habis Hanzali (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka sardaar banaey janey ka mashwara diya (to unhon-ne ye darkhaast ki ke kisi ko hamara sardaar bana dijiye (aur doosrey sahib ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne doosrey ( Qaaqaa bin Saeed bin Zaraara) ko banaey janey ka mashwara diya. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap ka maqsad sirf meri mukhalifat karna hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke meri niyat aap ki mukhalifat karna nahi hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein donon buzurgon ki awaz buland ho gaee. chunanche ye aayat nazil huii (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا ترفعوا أصواتكم‏) ''aey logon ! jo eman ley aaey ho apni awaz ko buland na karo. ''Allah taala ke irshad ( azeem ( tak. ibne-abii-mulaika ne bayan kya ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aayat ke utarney ke baad ye tariqa ikhtiyar kya aur ibne-Zubair ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apne naana ka zikr kya wo jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh arz kartey to itni aahisatagi se jaisey koi kaan mein baat karta hai yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baat sunai na deti to aap dobara poochhtey kya kaha,"
7303,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bimari mein farmaya Abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein Aaisha ne kaha ke maine jawaaban arz kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jagah khadey hongey to roney ki shiddat ki wjah se apni awaz logon ko nahi suna sakengey isliye aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke tum kaho ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki jagah khadey hongey to shiddat بکاء ki wjah se logon ko suna nahi sakengey, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko Namaz padhaaney ka hukm dein. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne aisa hi kya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bila shubah tum Yusuf paighambar ki sath waaliyaan ho? Abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein. baad mein Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke maine tum se kabhi kuchh bhalai nahi dekhi."
7304,"Uwemir Ajlani , Aasim bin Adi ke paas aaya aur kaha us shakhs ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai jo apni biwi ke sath kisi doosrey mard ko paaey aur usey qatl kar de, kya aap log maqtool ke badle mein usey qatl kar dengey? Aasim! mere liye aap, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq poochh dijiye. chunanche unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha lekin aap ne is tarah ke sawal ko na-pasand kya aur ma'yoob jaanaa. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne wapas aa kar unhein bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah ke sawal ko na-pasand kya hai. is par Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke Allah ki qasam! main khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jaaunga khair Uwemir aap ke paas aaey aur Aasim ke lot janey ke baad Allah Taala ne Quran Majeed ki aayat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil ki. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha ke tumharey barey mein Allah Taala ne Quran nazil kya hai, phir aap ne donon (miyaan beewii) ko bulaya. donon aagey badhey aur liaan kya. phir Uwemir ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! agar main usey ab bhi apne paas rakhta hun to uska matlab ye hai ke main jhoota hun chunanche us ne faurii apni biwi ko juda kar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne juda karne ka hukm nahi diya tha. phir liaan karne walon mein yahi tariqa raaij ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dekhtey raho iska bachcha laal laal past qad baamnii ki tarah ka paida ho to main samajhta hun ke wo Uwemir hi ka bachcha hai. Uwemir ne aurat par jhoota toofaan baandha aur agar saanwley rang ka badi aankh wala badey badey koolhon wala paida ho, jab main samjhoonga ke Uwemir sachcha hai phir us aurat ka bachcha us makruh sura ka yani jis mard se wo badnaam hui thi, usi sura ka paida hua."
7305,"Muhammad-bin-jubair-bin-mut'im ne mujh se is silsile mein zikr kya tha, phir main Malik ke paas gaya aur unse is hadis ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke main rawaana hua aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. itney mein unke darbaan yarfaa aaey aur kaha ke Usmaan, Abdur-Rehmaan, Zuber aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey hain, kya unhein ijazat di jaaey? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan. chunanche sab log andar aagey aur salam kya aur baith gaey, phir yarfaa ne aa kar puchha ke kya Ali aur Abbas ko ijazat di jaaey? un hazraat ko bhi andar bulaya. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ameerul-momineen ! mere aur zaalim ke darmyan faisla kar dijiye. aapas mein donon ne sakht kalaamii ki. is par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ki jamat ne kaha ke ameerul-momineen ! inke darmyan faisla kar dijiye taake donon ko aaraam hasil ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke sabr karo main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun jiski ijazat se aasman aur zameen qaaim hain. kya aap logon ko malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke hamari meeraas taqseem nahi hoti, ham jo kuchh chhodein wo sadqa hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is se khud apni zaat murad li thi. jamat ne kaha ke haan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. phir aap Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kaha ke main aap logon ko Allah ki qism deta hun. kya aap logon ko malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaayaa? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke haan. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske baad kaha ke phir main aap logon se us barey mein guftgu karta hun. Allah Taala ne apne rasool ka is maal mein se aik hissey makhsoos kya tha jo usney aap ke siwa kisi ko nahi diya. isliye ke Allah Taala farmata hai (ما أفاء الله على رسوله منهم فما أوجفتم) aayat. to ye maal khas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye tha, phir Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isey apne logon ko nazar andaz karke apne liye jama nahi kya aur na usey apni zaatii (ذاتی) jaaidaad banaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey aap logon ko bhi diya aur sab mein taqseem kya, yahan tak usmein se ye maal baqi reh gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se apne ghar walon ka saalaana kharch detey they, phir baqi apne qabzey mein ley letey they aur usey baitul-maal mein rakh kar aam musalmaanon ki zarooriyaat mein kharch kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zindagi bhar iske mutabiq amal kya. mein aap logon ko Allah ki qism deta hun kya aapko iska ilm hai? sahaba ne kaha ke haan, phir aap ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, mein aap donon hazraat ko bhi Allah ki qism deta hun kya aap logon ko iska ilm hai? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke haan. phir Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wafat di aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wali honey ki haisiyat se is par qabza kya aur is mein isi tarah amal kya jaisa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kartey they. aap donon hazraat bhi yahin maujood they. aap ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar ye baat kahi aur aap logon ka khayal tha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) is mamley mein khataakaar (خطاکار) hain aur Allah khub janta hai ke wo is mamley mein sachey aur nek aur sabse zyada haq ki pairwi karne waley they. phir Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko wafat di aur maine kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka wali hon is tarah maine bhi us jaaidaad ko apne qabzey mein do saal tak rakha aur is mein usi ke mutabiq amal karta raha jaisa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya tha. phir aap donon hazraat mere paas aaey aur aap logon ka mamla aik hi tha, koi ikhtilaf nahi tha. aap (Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) !) aaey apne bhai ke ladkey ki taraf se apni meeraas leney aur ye (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) apni biwi ki taraf se unke walid ki meeraas ki maang karne aaey. maine tum se kaha ke ye jaaidaad taqseem to nahi ho sakti lekin tum log chaho to main ehtimaam ke taur par aapko ye jaaidaad de dun lekin shart ye hai ke aap logon par Allah ka ahad aur uski meesaaq (waadaa) hai ke usko isi tarah kharch karogey jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha aur jis tarah Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya tha aur jis tarah maine apne vilaayet ke zamaney mein kya agar ye manzoor na ho to phir mujh se is maamle mein baat na karein. aap donon hazraat ne kaha ke is shart ke sath hamarey hawale jaaidaad kar dein. chunanche maine is shart ke sath aap ke hawale jaaidaad kar di thi. main aap logon ko Allah ki qism deta hun. kya maine un logon ko us shart ke sath jaaidaad di thi. jamat ne kaha ke haan. phir aap ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kaha, main aap logon ko Allah ki qism deta hun. kya maine jaaidaad aap logon ko us shart ke sath hawale ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. phir aap ne kaha, kya aap log mujh se iske siwa koi aur faisla chahtey hain. isliye us zaat ki qism jiske hukm se aasman aur zameen qaaim hain. us mein, iske siwa koi faisla nahi kar sakta yahan tak ke qiyamat aa jaey. agar aap log iska intizam nahi kar saktey to phir mere hawale kar do mein iska bhi intizam kar loonga."
7306,"maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina Munawra ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya hai? farmaya ke haan. falan jagah eir se falan jagah (sour) tak. is ilaqe ka darakht nahi kaataa jaeyga jisne in hadoo mein koi nai baat paida ki, is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam insanon ki laanat hai. Aasim ne bayan kya ke phir mujhey Moosaa-bin-Anas ne khabar di ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi bayan kya tha ke ''yaa kisi ne Deen mein bidat paida karne waley ko panah dii.''"
7307,"Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein lekar Haj kya to maine unhein ye kehtey suna ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ilm ko, iske baad ke tumhen diya hai aik dam se nahi utha lega balke usey is tarah khatm karega ke ulma ko unke ilm ke sath utha lega phir kuchh jaahi log baqi reh jaaeinge. unse fatwa puchha jaeyga aur wo fatwa apni raey ke mutabiq dengey. isliye wo logon ko gumrah karengey aur wo khud bhi gumrah hongey. phir maine ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan ki. unke baad Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne dobara Haj kya to Ummul-Momenin ne mujh se kaha ke bhaanjey Abdullah ke paas jao aur mere liye is hadis ko sun kar khub mazbut kar lo jo hadis tum ne mujh se unke waaste se bayan ki thi. chunanche main unke paas aaya aur maine unse puchha to unhon-ne mujh se wo hadis bayan ki. isi tarah jaisa ke wo pahley mujh se bayan kar chukey they. phir main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya aur unhein uski khabar di to unhein tajjub hua aur boliin ke Allah ki qism Abdullah-bin-Amr ne khub yad rakha."
7308,"maine abu-Waeil se puchha tum siiffiin ki ladai mein Sharik they? kaha ke haan, phir maine Sahal-bin-Haneef ko kehtey suna (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se Musa bin Ismail ne bayan kya. kaha ham se abu-Awana ne bayan kya, unse Aamash ne, unse abu-Waeil ne bayan kya ke Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) ne (jange-siiffiin ke mauqe par) kaha ke logon ! apne Deen ke muqable main apni raey ko be-haqeeqat samjho maine apne aapko abu-jandal (Raziallahu anhu) ke waaqie ke din (Suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) dekha ke agar mere andar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se hatney ki taqat hoti to main us din aap se nafarmani karta (aur kuffaare-Quraish ke sath un sharaait ko qabool na kartaa) aur ham ne jab kisi muhim par apni talwaarein kandhon par rakhiin (ladaaii shuru ki) to un talwaaron ki badoulet (بدولت) ham ko aik aasani mil gaee jisey ham pehchantey they magar is muhim mein (yani jange- siiffiin mein mushkil mein giraftaar hain donon taraf waley apney-apney dalaayel pesh kartey hain) abu-Aa'mash (ابواعمش) ne kaha ke abu-Waeil ne bataya ke main siiffiin mein maujood tha aur siiffiin ki ladai bhi kya buri ladai thi jis mein musalman aapas mein kat marey."
7309,"main bimar padaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. ye donon buzurg paidal chal kar aaey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahunchey to mujh par be-hoshi taarii thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur wuzu ka pani mujh par chhidkaa. us se mujhey fayda hua to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aur kabhi-kabhi Sufiyan ne ye alfaz bayan kiye ke maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! main apne maal ke barey mein kis tarah faisla karun. main apne maal ka kya karun? bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya, yahan tak ke meeraas ki aayat nazil hui."
7310,"aik khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ki tamam hadison mard le gaey. hamarey liye bhi aap koi din apni taraf se makhsoos kar dein jis mein ham aap ke paas aaein aur aap hamein wo taalimat dein jo Allah ne aapko sikhai hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke falan-falan din falan-falan jagah jama ho jao . chunanche auratein jama huin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas aaey aur unhein uski taleem di jo Allah ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sikhaya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se jo aurat bhi apni zindagi main apne teen bachchey aagey bhej degi. (yani unki wafat pa jaeygi) to wo uske liye dozakh se rukawat bin jaengey. is par unmein se aik khatun ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! do? unhon-ne is kalima ko do martabaa dohraayaa. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''haan do, do, do(2) bhi yahi darja rakhtey hain.''"
7311,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri ummat ka aik giroh hamesha ghalib rahega (is mein ilmi aur deeni ghalba bhi dakhil hai) yahan tak ke qiyamat aa jaeygi aur wo ghalib hi rahen gey.''
7312,"maine Muaawiya-bin-abii-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo khutba de rahe they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah jiske sath khair ka irada karta hai usey Deen ki samajh ata farma deta hai aur main to sirf taqseem karne wala hun aur deta Allah hai aur is ummat ka mamla hamesha durust rahega. yahan tak ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaey ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke) yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm aa pahunchey ."
7313,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat nazil hui (قل هو القادر على أن يبعث عليكم عذابا من فوقكم) ke ''kaho ke wo is par qaadir hai ke tum par tumharey uper se azab bhejey.'' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ke main terey ba azmat aur buzurg munh ki panah mangta hun. (أو من تحت أرجلكم) ''yaa tumharey paon ke nichey se'' (azaab bhejey) to is par phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ke main terey Mubarak munh ki panah mangta hon. phir jab ye aayat nazil huii                                   (أو يلبسكم شيعا ويذيق بعضكم بأس بعض‏) ke ''yaa tumhen firqon mein taqseem kar de aur tum mein se kuchh ko kuchh ka khof chakhaaey'' to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye donon aasan aur Sehal hain.
7314,aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke meri biwi ke yahan ladka paida hua hai jis ko main apna nahi samajhtaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumharey paas oont hain? unhon-ne kaha ke hain. malum kya ke unke rang kaisey hain? kaha ke surkh hain. puchha ke unmein koi khaakii bhi hai? unhon-ne kaha ji haan unmein khaakii bhi hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke phir kis tarah tum samajhtey ho ke is rang ka paida hua? unhon-ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! kisi rag ne ye rang kheench liya hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mumkin hai is bachchey ka rang bhi kisi rag ne kheench liya ho? aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko bachchey ke inkar karne ki ijazat nahi di.
7315,"aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein aur arz kya ke meri walida ne Haj karne ki nazar maana thi aur wo (adaaeygi se pahley hi ( wafat pa gaiin. kya main unki taraf se Haj kar loon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, unki taraf se Haj kar lo. tumhara kya khayal hai, agar tumhari walida par qarz hota to tum usey pura kartiin? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir us qarz ko bhi pura kar jo Allah Taala ka hai kyonke us qarz ka pura karna zyada zaroori hai."
7316,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''rashk 2 hi aadmiyon par ho sakta hai, aik wo jisey Allah ne maal diya aur usey (maal ko) raahe-haq mein lutaaney ki poori tarah taufeeq mili hoti hai aur doosra wo jisey Allah ne hikmat di hai aur uske zariey faisla karta hai aur uski taleem deta hai.''"
7317,umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aurat ke Imlaas ke mutaalliq (sahaaba se) poochha. ye us aurat ko kehtey hain jiske pet par mar diya gaya ( jabke wo haamla ho) ho aur uska naa-tamaam (adhooraa) bachcha gir gaya ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha aap logon mein se kisi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein koi hadis suni hai? maine kaha ke maine suni hai. puchha kya hadis hai? maine bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke aisi sura mein aik ghulam ya baandi taawaan ke taur par hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ab chhoot nahi saktey yahan tak ke tum ne jo hadis bayan ki hai is silsiley mein nijat ka koi zariey (yani koi shahadat ke waqei Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye hadis farmai thi) laao.
7318,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai ke usmein aik ghulam ya baandi ki taawaan hai. Hisham-bin-Urwa ke sath us hadis ko ibne-abi Zinaad ne bhi apne bap se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Mughira se riwayat kya."
7319,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak meri ummat is tarah pichhli ummaton ke mutabiq nahi ho jaeygi jaisey baalisht baalisht ke aur hath haath ke barabar hota hai.'' puchha gaya : ya Rasulullah ! agli ummaton se kon murad hain, paarsii aur nasrani ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir aur kaun.''"
7320,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum apne se pehli ummaton ki eik-eik baalisht aur eik-eik gaz mein ittaba (pairvi) karogey, yahan tak ke agar wo kisi goh ke suraakh mein dakhil huey hongey to tum usmein bhi unki ittaba (pairvi) karogey. ''ham ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya yahood w nasara murad hain? farmaya phir aur kaun."""
7321,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs bhi zulm ke sath qatl kya jaeyga iske ( gunah ka ( aik hissey Adam (Alaihissalam) ke pahley betey ( Qabeel ( par bhi padega.'' kabhi-kabhi Sufiyan ne is tarah bayan kya ke ''iske khoon kaa'' kyonke usi ne sabse pahley nahaq khoon ki buri rasm qaaim ki.
7322,"aik ganwaar (Qais-bin abi Hazim ya Qais-bin Hazim ya aur koii) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam par bait ki, phir Madina mein usko tapaaney lagi wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya. kehney laga : ya Rasulullah! meri bait tod dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya. wo phir aaya aur kehney laga : ya Rasulullah! meri bait fasakh kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir inkar kya. iske baad wo Madina se nikal kar apne jangal ko chala gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina lohaar ki bhattii ki tarah hai jo apni mail kuchail ko door kar deti hai aur kharey pakeeza maal ko rakh leti hai."
7323,"main Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko (Qur'aan majeed) padhaayaa karta tha. jab wo aakhiri Haj aaya jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya tha to Abdur-Rehman ne Mina mein mujh se kaha kash! tum ameerul-momineen ko aaj dekhtey jab unke paas aik shakhs aaya aur kaha ke falan shakhs kehta hai ke agar ameerul-momineen ka intiqal ho jaey to ham falan se bait kar lengey. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main aaj seh-pahar ko khadey ho kar logon ko khutba sunaunga aur unko daraaoongaa jo (aam musalmanon ke haq ko) hadap karna chahtey hain aur khud apni raey se ameer muntakhab karne ka irada rakhtey hain. maine arz kya ke aap aisa na karein kyonke mausam Haj mein har tarah ke na-waqif aur maamooli log jama ho jatey hain. ye sab kasarat se aap ki majlis mein jama ho jaeinge aur mujhey dar hai ke wo aap ki baat ka sahi matlab na samajh kar kuchh aur mana na kar lein aur usey munh dar munh udaatey phirein . isliye abhi thahrey rahiye. jab aap Madiney pahunchein jo daarul-hijrat aur daarus-sunnah hai to wahan aap ke mukhaatab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaaba, muhajireen w Ansar khalis aisey hi log mileingey wo aap ki baat ko yad rakhengey aur iska matlab bhi theek bayan karengey. is par ameerul-momineen ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! main Madina pahunch kar jo pahlaa khutba doonga usmein iska bayan karunga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham Madiney aaey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Juma ke din do-pahar dhaley baraamad huey aur khutba sunaya. unhon-ne kaha : Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sachcha rasool bana kar bheja aur aap par Quran utaaraa, is Quran mein rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat bhi thi."
7324,"ham Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they aur unke jism par kataan ke 2 kapdey geru mein rangey huey they. unhon-ne un hi kapdon mein naak saaf ki aur kaha waah waah dekho Abu-Hurera kataan ke kapdon mein naak saaf karta hai, ab aisa maaldaar ho gaya halanke maine apne aapko aik zamane mein aisa paya hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ke darmyan behosh ho kar gir padta tha aur guzarney wala meri gardan par ye samajh kar paon rakhta tha ke main paagal ho gaya hun, halanke mujhey junoon nahi hota tha, balke sirf bhook ki wjah se meri ye haalat ho jati thi."
7325,"kya aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eid mein gaey hain? kaha ke haan, mein us waqt kam-umr tha. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mujh ko itna nazdeek ka rishta na hota aur kam-umr na hota to aap ke sath kabhi nahi reh sakta tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se nikal kar us nishan ke paas aaey jo Kasir bin Salat ke makan ke paas hai aur wahan aap ne Namaz eid padhai phir khutba diya. unhon-ne azan aur iqamat ka zikr nahi kya, phir aap ne sadqa dene ka hukm diya to auratein apne kanon aur gardanon ki taraf hath badhaney lagiin zewaron ka sadqa dene ke liye, iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya, wo aaey aur sadqe mein mili hui chizon ko lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas wapas gaey."
7326,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quba mein tashrif latey they, kabhi paidal aur kabhi sawari par."
7327,unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tha ke mujhey intiqal ke baad meri sokanon ke sath dafn karna. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hujre mein dafn mat karna kyonke main pasand nahi karti ke meri aap ki aur beeviyon se zyada paakii bayan ki jaey.
7328,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aadmi bheja ke mujhey ijazat dein ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath dafn kya jaun. unhon-ne kaha ke haan, Allah ki qasam! mein unko ijazat deti hun. rawi ne bayan kya ke pahley jab koi sahabi unse wahan dafn honey ki ijazat maangtey to wo kelha deti thin ke nahi, Allah ki qasam! mein unke sath kisi aur ko dafn nahi honey doongii."
7329,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padh kar un gaanvon mein jatey jo Madina ki bulandi par hain, wahan pahunch jatey aur suraj buland rahtaa. awaalii Madina ka bhi yahi hukm hai aur Leis ne bhi is hadis ko Yunus se riwayat kya, usmein itna zyada hai ke ye gaaun Madina se teen char mail par hain."
7330,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein saa tumharey waqt ki mudd se aik mudd aur aik tehai mudd ka hota tha, phir saa ki miqdar badh gaee yani Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ke zamane mein wo char mudd ka ho gaya."
7331,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allah ! un Madina walon ke paimaane mein unhein barkat de aur unke saa aur mudd mein unhein barkat de.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad ahal Madina (ke saa w mudd ( se thi (madnii saa aur mudd ko bhi taareekhii azmat hasil hai).
7332,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Yahudi aik mard aur aik aurat ko lekar aaey jinhoney zina kya tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm diya aur unhein masjid ki aik jagah ke qareeb rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya jahan janazey rakhey jatey hain.
7333,Uhud pahaad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) rastey mein) dikhai diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye wo pahaad hai jo ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain. aey Allah ! Ibrahim ne Makka ko hurmat wala qarar diya tha aur main terey hukm se iske donon pathreeley kinaron ke darmyani ilaqe ko hurmat wala qarar deta hun. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Uhud ke mutaalliq ki hai.
7334,masjide-Nabawi ki qible ki taraf diwar aur member ke darmyan bakriyon ke guzarney jitna fasla tha.
7335,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere hujre aur mere member ke darmyan ki zameen jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai aur mera ye member mere hauz par hoga.''
7336,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghodon ki daud karaai aur wo ghodey chhodey gaey jo ghud daud ke liye taiyaar kiye gaey they, to unke daudney ka maidan maqam hafiya se saniiyatul-wadaa' tak tha aur jo taiyaar nahi kiye gaey they unke daudney ka maidan saniiyatul-wadaa' se masjid bani zuraiq tak tha aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi un logon mein they jinhoney muqaabley mein hissey liya tha."
7337,maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par) khutba detey ( suna.
7338,jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member se hamein Khattab kar rahe they.
7339,mere aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ye lagan rakhi jati thi aur ham donon us se aik sath nahatey they.
7340,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar aur Quraish ke darmyan mere us ghar mein bhai chaara karaya jo Madina Munawra mein hai.
7341,aur aap ne qabaayel banii-Sulaim ke liye aik mahina tak duaaey qunoot padhi jis mein unke liye baddua ki.
7342,mein Madina Munawra aaya aur Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) se meri mulaqat hui to unhon-ne kaha ke mere sath ghar chalo to main tumhen us piyaale mein pilaaunga jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyaa tha aur phir ham us Namaz padhney ki jagah Namaz padhengey jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi. chunanche main unke sath gaya aur unhon-ne mujhey sattu pilaya aur khajoor khilaaii aur maine unke Namaz padhney ki jagah Namaz padhi.
7343,mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas raat aik mere rab ki taraf se aaney wala aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt wadi aqeeq mein they aur kaha ke us Mubarak wadi mein Namaz padhiye aur kahey ke Umra aur Haj (ki niyat karta hun) aur Harun bin Ismail ne bayan kya ke ham se Ali ne bayan kya.
7344,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahal Najad ke liye maqam Qarn, Johfa ko ahale-Shaam (Syria) ke liye aur zul-Hulaifa ko ahal Madina ke liye meeqaat muqarrar kya. bayan kya ke maine ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aur mujhey malum hua hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ahal Yaman ke liye Yalamlam (meeqaat) hai aur Iraq ka zikr hua to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein Iraq nahi tha."
7345,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jabke aap maqam zul-Hulaifa mein padao kiye huey they, khuwab dikhaya gaya aur kaha gaya ke aap aik Mubarak wadi mein hain."
7346,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz mein ye dua rukoo se sar uthaney ke baad padhtey they ( اللهم ربنا ولك الحمد ( ''aey Allah ! hamarey rab terey hi liye tamam ta'reefein hain.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allah ! falan aur falan ko apni rehmat se door kar de.'' is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil ki ke aapko us maamle mein koi ikhtiyar nahi hai Allaah! unki tauba qabool kar ley ya unhein azab de ke bila shubah wo had se aagey badhney waley hain."
7347,unke aur Fatima binte-rasoolullaah (Alaihissalam) ke ghar aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke tum log tahajjud ki Namaz nahi padhtey . Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamari jaanein Allah ke hath mein hain to jab wo hamein uthana chahey to ham ko utha dega. joon hi maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye kaha to aap peeth mod kar wapas janey lagey aur koi jawab nahi diya lekin wapas jatey huey aap apni raan par hath mar rahe they aur keh rahe they ( وكان الإنسان أكثر شىء جدلا‏ ( ''aur insan bada hi jhagdaaloo hai'' agar koi tumharey paas raat mein aaey to ( Tariq ( kahlaaeyga aur Quran mein jo ( والطارق (ka lafz aaya hai us se murad sitaara hai aur) Saqib ( ba-maanaa chamaktaa hua. Arab log aag jalaaney waley se kehtey hain ( ثقب نارك ( yani aag roshan kar. us se lafz ( Saqib ( hai.
7348,"ham masjide-Nabawi mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke yahudiyon ke paas chalo. chunanche ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey. jab ham unke madrase tak pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar unhein awaz di aur farmaya, aey yahood! Islam lao to tum salamat rahogey . is par yahudiyon ne kaha ke abul-Qaasim ! aap ne Allah ka hukm pahuncha diya. rawi ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara unse farmaya ke yahi mera maqsad hai, Islam lao to tum salamat rahogey . unhon-ne kaha abul-Qaasim ! aap ne Allah ka paigham pahuncha diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi baat teesri baar kahi aur farmaya, jaan lo ke saari zameen Allah aur uske rasool ki hai aur main chahta hun ke tumhen us jagah se bahar kar dun. to tum mein se jo koi apni jaaidaad ke badley mein koi qeemat paata ho to usey bech ley warna jaan lo ke zameen Allah aur uske rasool ki hai (tum ko ye Shahar chhodnaa hoga ( ."
7349,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din Nuh (Alaihissalam) ko laya jaeyga aur unse puchha jaeyga, kya tum ne Allah ka paigham pahuncha diya tha? wo arz karengey ke haan, aey rab! phir unki ummat se puchha jaeyga ke kya unhon-ne tumhen Allah ka paigham pahuncha diya tha? wo kahengey ke hamarey paas koi daraane wala nahi aaya. Allah Taala Nuh (Alaihissalam) se poochhega , tumharey gawah kon hain? Nuh (Alaihissalam) arz karengey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unki ummat phir tumhen laya jaeyga aur tum log unke haq mein shahadat doge , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhi ( ‏‏‏‏وكذلك جعلناكم أمة وسطا‏ ( ''aur isi tarah ham ne tumhen darmyani ummat banaya. ''kaha ke) beech ( ba-maanaa ( adl ( (beech kii) hai, taake tum logon ke liye gawah bano aur rasool tum par gawah baney. Ishaq-bin-Mansur se Jafar bin Aun ne riwayat kya, kaha ham se Aamash ne bayan kya, unse Abu-Saleh ne, unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi hadis bayan farmai."
7350,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Adi Ansari ke aik sahib saudaa bin-Aziiya ko khaibar ka aamil bana kar bheja to wo umda qism ki khajoor wsool karke laey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein aisi hi hain? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! ham aisi aik saa khajoor 2 saa ( kharaab ( khajoor ke badley khareed letey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na kya karo balke (jins ko jins ke badley) barabar barabar mein khareedo, ya yun karo ke raddi khajoor naqdii bech dalo phir ye khajoor iske badley khareed lo, isi tarah har cheez ko jo tol kar bikti hai iska hukm un hi chizon ka hai jo naap kar bikti hain."
7351,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Adi Ansari ke aik sahib saudaa bin-Aziiya ko khaibar ka aamil bana kar bheja to wo umda qism ki khajoor wsool karke laey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein aisi hi hain? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! ham aisi aik saa khajoor 2 saa ( kharaab ( khajoor ke badley khareed letey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na kya karo balke (jins ko jins ke badley) barabar barabar mein khareedo, ya yun karo ke raddi khajoor naqdii bech dalo phir ye khajoor iske badley khareed lo, isi tarah har cheez ko jo tol kar bikti hai iska hukm un hi chizon ka hai jo naap kar bikti hain."
7352,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Hakim koi faisla apne ijtihaad se karey aur faisla sahi ho to usey dohra sawab milta hai aur jab kisi faisle mein ijtihaad karey aur ghalati kar jaey to usey ikehraa sawab milta hai (ijtihaad ka ( bayan kya ke phir maine ye hadis Abu-Bakar bin-Amr bin Hazam se bayan ki to unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujh se abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne isi tarah bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur Abdul-Azeez bin-Muttalib ne bayan kya, unse Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr ne bayan kya, unse abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah bayan farmaya."
7353,"ham se Musaddad bin musarhid ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Juraij ne, unse Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne, unse Ubaid-bin-Umair ne bayan kya ke abu-Moosa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se (milney kii) ijazat chahi aur ye dekh kar ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) mashghool hain aap jaldi se wapas chaley gaey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kya maine abhi Abdullah bin Qais (abu-Moosa (Raziallahu anhu)) ki awaz nahi suni thi ? unhein bula lo. chunanche unhein bulaya gaya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke aisa kyon kya? (ke jaldi wapas ho gaey ( unhoney kaha ke hamein hadis mein is ka hukm diya gaya hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke is hadis par gawah lao warna main tumharey sath ye (sakhtii) karunga. chunanche Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Ansar ki majlis mein gaey. unhoney kaha ke is ki gawahi ham mein sab se chhota dey sakta hai. chunanche Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha ke hamein darbaare-nabawii se is ka hukm diya jata tha. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye hukm mujhey malum nahi tha 'mujhey bazar ke kaamon khareed-farokht ne is hadis se ghaafil rakhaa."
7354,"tum samajhtey ho ke Abu-Hurera Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat zyada hadis bayan kartey hain, Allah ke huzoor mein sab ko jana hai. baat ye thi ke main aik miskeen shakhs tha aur pet bharney ke baad har waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rehta tha lekin muhajireen ko bazar ke karobar mashghool rakhtey they aur Ansar ko apne maalon ki dekh-bhaal masroof rakhti thi. main aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kon apni chadar phailaaeyga, yahan tak ke main apni baat poori kar loon aur phir wo apni chadar samet ley aur uske baad kabhi mujh se suni hui koi baat na bhooley. chunanche maine apni chadar jo mere jism par thi, phaila di aur us zaat ki qism jisne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath bheja tha phir kabhi main aapki koi hadis jo aap se suni thi, nahi bhoolaa."
7355,maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo ibne-Sayyaad ke waqia par Allah ki qism khaatey they. maine unse kaha ke aap Allah ki qism khaatey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Allah ki qism khaatey dekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par koi inkar nahi farmaayaa.
7356,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ghodey teen tarah ke logon ke liye hain. aik shakhs ke liye unka rakhna sawab ka kaam hai, doosrey ke liye barabar barabar na azab na sawab aur teesrey ke liye wabaale-jaan hain. jiske liye wo ajr hain ye wo shakhs hai jisne usey Allah ke rastey ke liye baandh kar rakha aur uski rassii charaa-gaah mein lambi chhod di to wo ghoda jitni door tak charaah gaah mein ghoom kar charega wo Malik ki nekiyon mein taraqqi ka zariia' hoga aur agar ghodey ne us daraaz rassii ko bhi tudwa liya aur aik ya 2 daud us ne lagai to iske nishaanaate-qadam aur uski leed bhi Malik ke liye baaise-ajr w sawab hogi aur agar ghoda kisi nehar se guzra aur us ne nehar ka pani pi liya, Malik ne usey pilaaney ka koi irada nahi kya tha tab bhi Malik ke liye ye ajr ka baais hoga aur aisa ghoda apne Malik ke liye sawab hota hai aur doosra shakhs barabar barabar wala hota hai jo ghodey ko izhar be niyaazii ya apne bachao ki gharaz se baandhtaa hai aur uski pusht aur gardan par Allah ke haq ko bhi nahi bhooltaa to ye ghoda uske liye na azab hai na sawab aur tesraa wo shakhs hai jo ghodey ko fakhr aur dikhawey ke liye baandhtaa hai to ye uske liye wabaale-jaan hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne is silsile mein mujh par is jaame' aur naadir aayat ke siwa aur kuchh nahi nazil farmaya hai) فمن يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره‏ ( '' to jo koi aik zarra barabar bhi bhalai karega wo usey dekhega aur jo koi aik zarra barabar bhi burai karega wo usey dekhega .''"
7357,"aik khatun ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se Muhammad ne bayan kya yani ibne- Aqba ne, kaha ham se Fuzel bin Sulaiman numairii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Mansoor bin Abdur-Rehman bin Sheba ne bayan kya, unse unki walida ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ke aik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se haiz ke mutaalliq puchha ke us se ghusl kis tarah kya jaaey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mashk laga hua aik kapda lekar us se paakii hasil kar. us aurat ne puchha : ya Rasulullah! main us se paakii kis tarah hasil karoongii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us se paakii hasil karo. unhon-ne phir puchha ke kis tarah paakii hasil karun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir wahi jawab diya ke paakii hasil karo. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mansha samajh gaee aur us aurat ko maine apni taraf kheench liya aur unhein tariqa bataya ke paakii se aap ka matlab ye hai ke us kapdey ko khoon ke maqaamon par pher taake khoon ki badboo hat jaey."
7358,"umme-Hufaid binte- Haris bin huzn (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghi aur paneer aur bhunaa hua saandaa hadiye mein bheja Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye cheezein qabool farma lein aur aap ke dastar-khuwaan par unhein khaya gaya lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (saandey ko) hath nahi lagaayaa, jaisey aapko pasand na ho aur agar wo haram hota to aap ke dastar-khuwaan par na khaya jata aur na aap khaney ke liye kehtey."
7359,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs kachchi lehsun ya piyaz khaaey wo ham se door rahe ya (ye farmaya ke) hamari masjid se door rahe aur apne ghar mein betha rahe (yahaan tak ke wo bo khatm ho jaey) aur aap ke paas aik Tabaaq laya gaya jis mein sabziyaan thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein boo mehsus ki, phir aapko usmein rakhi hui sabziyon ke mutaalliq bataya gaya to aap ne apne kuchh sahabi ki taraf jo aap ke sath they ishara karke farmaya ke unke paas ley jao lekin jab un sahabi ne usey dekha to unhon-ne bhi usey khana pasand nahi kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par unse farmaya ke tum kha lo kyonke main jis se sargoshi karta hun tum us se nahi kartey. (aap ki murad farishton se thi) Saeed bin Kasir bin afeer ne jo imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke Shekh hain, Abdullah-bin Wahab se is hadis mein yun riwayat kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas handi laai gaee jis mein tarkaariyaan thin aur Leis w abu-Safwaan Abdullaah-bin-Saeed umwii ne bhi us hadis ko Yunus se riwayat kya lekin unhon-ne handi ka qissa nahi bayan kya, ab main nahi janta ke handi ka qissa hadis mein dakhil hai ya Zohri ne badha diya hai."
7360,"aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaiin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik hukm diya. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! agar main aapko na paon to phir kya karoongii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab mujhey na paanaa to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jaanaa. Humaidii ne Ibrahim bin Sad se ye izafa kya ke ghaaliban khatun ki murad wafat thi. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Humaidii ne is riwayat mein Ibrahim bin Sad se itna badhaya hai ke aapko na paaun, us se murad ye hai ke aap ki wafat ho jaey."
7361,"wo Madiney mein Quraish ki aik jamat se hadis bayan kar rahe they. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kab ahbaar ka zikr kya aur farmaya jitney log ahle-kitab se hadison naql kartey hain un sab mein Kab ahbaar bahut sachey they aur bawajud iske kabhi kabhii unki baat jhoot nikalti thi, ye matlab nahi hai ke Kab ahbaar jhoot boltey they."
7362,"ahle-kitab Taurait Ibranii zaban mein padhtey they aur uski tafseer musalmanon ke liye arabii mein kartey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ahle-kitab ki na tasdeeq karo aur na unki takzeeb karo kyonke ham eman laey Allah par aur is par jo ham par nazil hua aur jo ham se pahley tum par nazil hua aakhir aayat tak jo sura al-Baqara mein hai."
7363,tum ahle-kitab se kisi cheez ke barey mein kyon poochhtey ho jabke tumhari kitab jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hui wo taaza bhi hai aur mehfooz bhi aur tumhen us ne bata bhi diya ke ahle-kitab ne apna Deen badal daala aur Allah ki kitab mein tabdili kar di aur usey apne hath se az khud bana kar likha aur kaha ke ye Allah ki taraf se hai taake iske zariey duniya ka thoda sa maal kamaa lein. tumharey paas ( Quran w hadis ka ( jo ilm hai wo tumhen unse poochhney se mana karta hai. Allah ki qism ! main to nahi dekhta ke ahle-kitab mein se koi tum se iske barey mein poochhta ho jo tum par nazil kya gaya ho.
7364,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab tumharey dil miley rahen Quran padho aur jab tum mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to us se door ho jao .''
7365,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tak tumharey dilon mein ittihaad w ittifaq ho Quran padho aur jab ikhtilaf ho jaey to us se door ho jaao.'' aur Yazid-bin-Harun waastii ne Harun Aawar se bayan kya, unse abu-Imran ne bayan kya, unse Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya."
7366,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt qareeb aaya to ghar mein bahut se sahaba maujood they, jin mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aao main tumharey liye aik aisa maktoob likh dun ke iske baad tum kabhi gumrah na ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aao main tumharey liye aik aisa maktoob likh dun ke iske baad tum kabhi gumrah na ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takleef mein mubtala hain, tumharey paas Allah ki kitab hai aur yahi hamarey liye kafi hai. ghar ke logon mein bhi ikhtilaf ho gaya aur aapas mein bahas karne lagey. unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb ( likhney ka saman ( kar do. wo tumharey liye aisi cheez likh dengey ke iske baad tum gumrah nahi hogey aur kuchh ne wahi baat kahi jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) keh chukey they. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas log ikhtilaf w bahas zyada karne lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas se hat jao. Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke sabse bhari museebat to wo they jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur us nawishta likhwaaney ke beech rukawat baney, yani jhagdaa aur shor."
7367,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khalis Haj ka ehram baandha iske sath Umre ka nahi baandhaa. Ata ne bayan kya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 4 Zil-Hijja ki subah ko aaey aur jab ham bhi hazir huey to aap ne hamein hukm diya ke ham halal ho jayen aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke halal ho jao aur apni beeviyon ke paas jao. Ata ne bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke un par ye zaroori nahi qarar diya balke sirf halal kya, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke ham mein ye baat ho rahi hai ke Arfa pahunchne mein sirf panch din reh gaey hain aur phir bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apni aurton ke paas janey ka hukm diya hai, kya ham Arafaat us haalat mein jayen ke mazi ya mani hamarey zakar (khaas ang) se tapak rahi ho. Ata ne kaha ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne hath se ishara kya ke is tarah mazi tapak rahi ho, usko hilaayaa. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya, tumhen malum hai ke main tum mein Allah se sabse zyada darney wala hun, tum mein sabse zyada sachcha hun aur sabse zyada nek hun aur agar mere paas qurbani ka janwar (qurbaanii ka jaanwar) na hota to main bhi halal ho jata, to tum bhi halal ho jao. agar mujhey wo baat pahley se malum ho jati jo baad mein malum hui to main qurbani ka janwar sath na laataa. chunanche ham halal ho gaey aur ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat suni aur aap ki itaat ki."
7368,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maghrib ki Namaz se pahley bhi Namaz padho aur teesri martaba mein farmaya ke jiska ji chahey kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pasand nahi kartey they ke usey log lazimi sunnat bana lein.
7369,"mujh se Urwa bin Musaiyab aur Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullaah-bin-abdullaah ne bayan kya aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ke jab tohmat lagaaney walon ne un par tohmat lagai thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali-bin abii-Taalib, Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya kyonke is maamle mein wahi us waqt tak nahi aai thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne-ahale-khaana ko juda karne ke silsile mein unse mashwara lena chahtey they, to Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne wahi mashwara diya jo unhein malum tha yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahale-khaana ki Bara't (Tauba) ka lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne aap par koi pabandi to Aaiz nahi ki hai aur uske siwa aur bahut si auratein hain, baandi se aap malum farma lein, wo aap se sahi baat bata degi. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya tum ne koi aisi baat dekhi hai jis se shuba hota hai. unhon-ne kaha ke maine iske siwa aur kuchh nahi dekha ke wo kam Umr ladki hain, aata goondh kar bhi so jati hain aur padaus ki bakri aa kar usey kha jati hai, iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey aur farmaya, aey musalmaanon ! mere mamley mein us se kon nimatney ga jiski aziyatein ab mere ahal khaana tak pahunch gaee hain. Allah ki qism ! maine unke barey mein bhalai ke siwa aur kuchh nahi jana hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki paak daamanii ka qissa bayan kya aur abu-Usama ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se bayan kya."
7370,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab kya aur Allah ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya ''tum mujhey un logon ke barey mein mashwara detey ho jo mere ahal khaana ko badnaam kartey hain halanke unke barey mein mujhey koi buri baat kabhi nahi malum hui. Urwa se riwayat hai, unhon-ne ham se bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko jab is waaqie ka ilm hua (ke kuchh log unhein badnaam kar rahe hain) to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : ya Rasulullah! kya mujhey aap apne walid ke ghar janey ki ijazat dengey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat di aur unke sath ghulam ko bhejaa. Ansar mein se aik sahib Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kahaa سبحانك ما يكون لنا أن نتكلم بهذا ، Mina padhi. سبحانك هذا بهتان عظيم ''terii zaat paak hai, aey Allaah! hamarey liye munasib nahi ke ham is tarah ki baatein karein teri zaat paak hai, ye to bahut bada bohtan hai.''"
